udes. Rebasing assumes exclusions distribute proportionally across appropriations.", "s": "S_DEFAULT"}, {"r": 60, "c": 0, "k": "v", "p": "Section 6 - Cross-Appropriation Addbacks (non-OMN, post-rebase)  [BARS 4-7 source]", "s": "S_TITLE_SECTION"}, {"r": 61, "c": 1, "k": "v", "p": "Addback bars are FPDS MRO obligations funded from appropriations OTHER than OMN. Uses post-rebase values so the sum lands cleanly at the Services MRO TAM (bar 8) net of the OMN slice.", "s": "S_DEFAULT"}, {"r": 62, "c": 0, "k": "v", "p": "Step", "s": "S_BOLD"}, {"r": 62, "c": 1, "k": "v", "p": "Bar", "s": "S_BOLD"}, {"r": 62, "c": 2, "k": "v", "p": "$M (rebased)", "s": "S_BOLD"}, {"r": 62, "c": 3, "k": "v", "p": "Formula", "s": "S_BOLD"}, {"r": 62, "c": 4, "k": "v", "p": "Source / note", "s": "S_BOLD"}, {"r": 63, "c": 0, "k": "v", "p": "BAR 4", "s": "S_BOLD"}, {"r": 63, "c": 1, "k": "v", "p": "+FPDS obligations from OPN (Other Procurement, Navy)", "s": "S_BOLD"}, {"r": 63, "c": 2, "k": "f", "p": "MRO_TAS_OPN_FY25*(NAVY_TAM_SVC+CG_TAM_SVC)/MRO_TAS_TOTAL_FY25", "s": "S_NUM_TOTAL"}, {"r": 63, "c": 3, "k": "v", "p": "MRO_TAS_OPN_FY25 * rebase factor", "s": "S_DEFAULT"}, {"r": 63, "c": 4, "k": "v", "p": "Modernization procurement; includes BA-7 equipment installs, BA-8 spares, BA-1 ships support.", "s": "S_DEFAULT"}, {"r": 64, "c": 0, "k": "v", "p": "BAR 5", "s": "S_BOLD"}, {"r": 64, "c": 1, "k": "v", "p": "+FPDS obligations from USCG (OE + AC&I)", "s": "S_BOLD"}, {"r": 64, "c": 2, "k": "f", "p": "MRO_TAS_USCG_FY25*(NAVY_TAM_SVC+CG_TAM_SVC)/MRO_TAS_TOTAL_FY25", "s": "S_NUM_TOTAL"}, {"r": 64, "c": 3, "k": "v", "p": "MRO_TAS_USCG_FY25 * rebase factor", "s": "S_DEFAULT"}, {"r": 64, "c": 4, "k": "v", "p": "Coast Guard cutter sustainment + ISVS + routine OE depot work.", "s": "S_DEFAULT"}, {"r": 65, "c": 0, "k": "v", "p": "BAR 6", "s": "S_BOLD"}, {"r": 65, "c": 1, "k": "v", "p": "+FPDS obligations from RDT&E, Defense-Wide", "s": "S_BOLD"}, {"r": 65, "c": 2, "k": "f", "p": "MRO_TAS_RDTE_DW_FY25*(NAVY